# NASDAQ small-cap screener — self-hosted cron option.
# Runs every weekday at 06:00 in the SERVER's local time zone; main.py itself
# skips weekends/holidays via the market calendar. Set the server TZ to America/New_York
# (or adjust the hour) so this fires at 6:00 AM ET, before pre-market activity.
#
# Install with:  crontab cron/screener.crontab
0 6 * * 1-5 cd /path/to/project && python src/main.py >> logs/screener.log 2>&1
